**US-003 Complete.** 

Implemented router with in-memory rate limiter:

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `canRequest(providerId)` | Checks if provider has RPM slots available |
| `recordRequest(providerId)` | Logs timestamp for rate limiting |
| `resolveModel(assetType)` | Returns highest priority available model (filters by assetType, model active, provider active, RPM slot) |
| `nextSlotDelay(providerId)` | Calculates ms until next slot opens |

Rate limiting uses 60-second sliding window via `Map<string, number[]>` storing request timestamps.

